{
  "stem": "13469.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There are loads of things in my memory, which I just can't recall until somebody mentions it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when somebody mentions it, then I can remember it quite clearly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So that was the second way of recalling things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The third way was that I've got all these documents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't remember that I ever went to a Jewish school in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I've got a report to prove it here, so I must have done.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I have loads of other photographs of the olden days, and the days in Holland, and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they have obviously stimulated me to remembering lots of things that I'd forgotten before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was the third way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the fourth way is by reading books and talking to other survivors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when I meet other survivors, they remind me of certain things that they experienced.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then I say, oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And, you know, it-- it isn't that we're trying to make our story better or enlarge upon our story.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It's just that I've forgotten certain things, until, again, another survivor says, you remember, in Westerbork, we had showers and all this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I'd forgotten that we had showers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Well, that wasn't a typical thing, but something like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They would say, we had this in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then, I can remember it quite clearly again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those were four different ways, which I [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very grateful for that question came in on how I was able to remember it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So now, when we go to the yellow stars, I don't remember it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I've now found out from reading the books that we actually had to pay money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to buy the yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
